## 🗄️ MySQL Staging

All results were staged into a local MySQL database (`vortex_db`) using SQLAlchemy, enabling direct Power BI connectivity:

```
vortex_db
├── clean_transactions   → 397,884 rows
├── frequent_itemsets    → 226 rows
└── association_rules    → 56 rows
```

