---

## 💡 Key Learnings

- Real-world data is messy — 26% of the dataset had to be dropped before mining
- Concept Hierarchies are the difference between noise and insight
- FP-Growth is significantly more practical than Apriori at scale
- Association rules are only useful when translated into business actions — the algorithm is the easy part

